Package: flatpak-automatic
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, flatpak, systemd, python3, python3-yaml, python3-dbus
Recommends: python3-apprise
Description: Secure, systemd-native automation for Flatpak updates
 A secure, systemd-native automation wrapper for Flatpak updates. It
 features Snapper-integrated atomic rollbacks, multi-channel alerting
 (Apprise, Mail, Webhooks, Desktop), and supports both system-wide and
 rootless user-level execution. Designed for reliability and ease of
 use, it ensures your Flatpak environment remains current and resilient.

